reviewText: My son loves the DVD, but the last song (Chu Chua ), is not complete, however, it looks like that's the way the content was intended to end.  All in all, it's a good DVD.

I bought the DVD for my son as he loves the song Chu Chuah and according to the list of songs the DVD had that song but when I received the package it was missing that song instead of 15 song it had 14
